OL,5, British playwright Edward Bond, who was
OL,6, known for his social commentary, died  
OL,7, on Sunday at the age of 89.            
OL,9,FThe dramatist penned more than 50 plays
OL,10,Fin his career, including Lear and The  
OL,11,FSea.                                   
OL,13,FHis play Saved, set on a south London  
OL,14,Fcouncil estate, sparked controversy for
OL,15,Fits portrayals of violence, which      
OL,16,Finitially saw it banned when first     
OL,17,Fstaged in 1965.                        
OL,19,FActor Samuel West described him as "a  
OL,20,Ftheatrical giant" in a post on X.      
